@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nowcoa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.07 - (wp.sin(tmp + 0.16) / 0.75))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v2 + 0.07 - v2 + 0.22)))
    v0 = wp.exp(v1)
    v2 = 0.07
    v0 = 0.77
    data[tid] = v0
